## 🚀 Deployment

This site is optimized for **GitHub Pages**. To deploy your own copy:

1. **Fork this repository** or create a new one.
2. **Copy the `index.html`** file into the root of your repo.
3. (Optional) Add your custom `cv.pdf` to an `assets/` folder and your profile picture to `images/`.
4. Go to your repository **Settings** → **Pages**.
5. Under "Branch", select `main` and save.
6. Your site will be live at `https://<your-username>.github.io/<repo-name>/` within a few minutes.

Alternatively, you can serve it locally with any static server:

```bash
# Using Python 3
python -m http.server 8000

# Using Node.js (serve)
npx serve.
